            <title>LG 香港推新窗口式變頻冷氣，智能冷氣及空氣潔淨產品系列</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-air-conditioner</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 06:44:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301895</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 電子今日在香港發佈全新智能家居產品系列，重點是搭載最新節能技術及智慧控制的 LG 窗口式變頻冷氣機，同時展示多款空氣潔淨產品，包括 LG PuriCare AeroBooster 和雙迴轉變頻抽濕機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>智慧節能冷氣技術，實現全面環保節能</h2><p>發佈會重點在於 LG 窗口式變頻冷氣機，搭載先進 AI 智能節能控制技術，能根據環境變化自動調整製冷強度，確保在炎夏高温下仍能提供舒適涼爽體驗。據 LG 技術專家介紹，冷氣機具備多檔風速調控及智慧温控功能，可減少高達 49% 的能源消耗，特別適合香港地區夏季長期開機使用的需求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301910" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301911" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301912" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>冷氣機亦兼顧環保考量，採用符合國際標準的 R32 冷媒，減少對臭氧層的破壞，同時優化能效比（EER），在節能與性能之間達到最佳平衡。與此同時，產品內建的智能空氣流動系統，可將冷氣均勻分佈至房間各個角落，避免冷風直吹人體，增強整體舒適度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301913" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>智能空氣管理，多元化應用選擇</h2><p>為了滿足不同家庭和空間的需求，LG 窗口式變頻冷氣機共推出 5 種型號，從 0.75 匹到 2.5 匹不等，涵蓋單身公寓至大型客廳的應用場景。特別是在睡眠模式下，冷氣機會自動降低運行音量，並透過智慧控温功能維持涼爽而安靜的環境。</p><p>冷氣機內建遠程控制功能，透過 LG ThinQ 應用程式，使用者可以隨時掌控設備運行狀態及温度設置，特別是在外出時提前啟動或關閉冷氣，大大提升操作便利性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2></h2><h2>空氣潔淨產品同步亮相  創造清新健康空間</h2><p>除冷氣機外，LG 亦展示了多款空氣淨化產品，包括 LG PuriCare AeroBooster 智能空氣清新機和雙迴轉變頻抽濕機，這些設備能有效清除空氣中的懸浮微粒及異味，特別適合空氣質素堪憂的都市環境。</p><p>LG PuriCare AeroBooster 採用 360 度環繞送風系統，內建 HEPA 過濾及活性炭除臭濾網，能去除 99.9% 的過敏原及 PM2.5 微粒。特有的 Pet Mode 專為飼養寵物的家庭設計，能有效去除毛髮及異味，提升空氣潔淨度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-scaled.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>在抽濕方面，LG 雙迴轉變頻抽濕機，配備高效智能濕度控制，可自動感應環境濕度並動態調節除濕力度。內建抗菌濾網，確保在保持乾燥同時，有效阻隔黴菌及塵蟎滋生，適合在潮濕多雨的季節使用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-493x580.jpeg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-493x580.jpeg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-scaled.jpeg 765w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></a></p><p>LG 產品策略聚焦於整合冷氣及空氣管理技術，全面提升室內環境品質。</p><p>LG 表示，未來公司將繼續推動家電智能化升級，透過引入更多 AI 技術，讓智慧家庭不只節能，更能有效應對現代都市空氣污染問題。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/">LG 香港推新窗口式變頻冷氣，智能冷氣及空氣潔淨產品系列</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
